Package main

Class Vector2d

java.lang.Object
main.Vector2d
public final class Vector2d
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents a two dimensional vector and contains some methods for operating in a R^2 vector space.
Author:
David Voigt

    • limit

      public static void limit​(Vector2d v, double limit, Vector2d ret)
      Limits a given vector by a given value and stores the result in the second given vector instance. If the length of the given vector exceeds the limit set by the given value the vector length is being limited to that value otherwise the vector will be left unchanged.
      Parameters:
      v - Vector who is to be limited.
      limit - Limiting value.
      ret - Vector instance where the result will be stored in.

    • limit
